<h2 id='payments-investors-post-test-account-topup'><code>🧪 POST /test/account/topup</code></h2><h3 id='payments-investors-code-post-test-account-topup-code-description'>Description</h3>
<p>Simulate depositing cash into any bank account managed on the Goji platform.</p>

<p>For an investor account the payment reference must start with <code>ISA</code> if the funds are to be deposited to the ISA account.</p>

<aside class="notice">
Please note this is a test endpoint and is only available in the sandbox environment.
</aside>
<pre class="highlight http tab-http"><code><span class="nf">POST</span> <span class="nn">/test/account/topup</span> <span class="k">HTTP</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="m">1.1</span>
<span class="na">Host</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s">api-sandbox.goji.investments</span>
<span class="na">Content-Type</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s">application/json</span>
<span class="na">Authorization</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s">Basic ...</span>

<span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="s2">"amount"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
        </span><span class="s2">"amount"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">amount</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
        </span><span class="s2">"currency"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">"GBP"</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="p">},</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="s2">"accountNumber"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">"accountNumber"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="s2">"sortCode"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">"sortCode"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="s2">"paymentReference"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">"paymentReference"</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">

</span></code></pre><h3 id='payments-investors-code-post-test-account-topup-code-request'>Request</h3>
